是主动去破坏老爷子的灵，行为恶劣，那我们纵观整个一人之下的故事，吕良等人偷挖并侮辱张楚岚爷爷的尸体，冯宝宝在比赛期间，多次出现偷袭绑架埋人的行为，老天师下药操纵比赛，临时工帮肖自在隐瞒杀人情况，陈金魁非法拘禁王也等等，那么多违法犯罪的事情，论性质应该更加恶劣了吧。 王并确实品行不行，但是这说到底也是道德问题，不涉及法律吧。法律是对人最低的道德要求，一人之下更多的人明明是违反法律，也没有得到惩罚，却不见被观众反对，只有王并在被骂，这不是一种双标么？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3e8822c35b1c62ad39aebfa606ee4749_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "133 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/446684830"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IvqfE5djElvFdEAMaCDYxNTQxODAyINH054EGMAU4pgFAFnIJNDQ2Njg0ODMweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1614538887.210066", "card_id": "Q_446808495", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 77}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价微博之夜张艺兴的唱跳舞台《Joker》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "官方版： cr:CHERE_MAMIE_for_Lay 的微博"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-cac1bec6696cc23cc4658fb07961fef2_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "133 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/446808495"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IvqfE5djElvFdEAMaCDYxNTY5MjI2IND764EGMAQ4bEAXcgk0NDY4MDg0OTV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1614538887.2104592", "card_id": "Q_445431076", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 56}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "对钟汉良、谭松韵主演的《锦心似玉》，你想说点什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "130 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/445431076"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IvqfE5djElvFdEAMaCDYxMjYzNDI4INzFw4EGMAE4WUAYcgk0NDU0MzEwNzZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1614538887.210704", "card_id": "Q_445392303", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 3